Knowledge Center
Wholesale Banking

The Wholesale Banking Division of the UBA Ghana provides a full range of solutions, including short to medium-term lending, structured finance and transaction banking with strong support systems and processes to meet corporate banking requirements.

Besides traditional lending, we also engineer tailor-made solutions with aid of our world-class technology platforms to meet constantly changing needs of companies.

Dedicated Relationship Managers are available to assist companies on all their banking requirements.

For more information, click on any of the product categories below:

  • Cash Management Services

  • Trade Services

  • Loans

  • Distributor Finance

  • Structured Finance
